{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fa9f55a901","title":"对《百花齐放，百家争鸣》一文的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6e45e9188a","index":0,"year":1956,"month":6,"day":8,"articleId":"fa9f55a901"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/36-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji36":{"comments":[{"id":"3d289bafad","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在陆定-1956年6月7日为送审《百花齐放，百家争鸣》的讲话稿给毛泽东的信上。信中说：因为有二百个科学家集中北京起草科学规划，李富春提议向他们讲一次百花齐放、百家争鸣的政策。少奇同志指定我去讲。讲稿起草后，中宣部讨论了两次，后又根据恩来同志的意见作了修改。5月26日在两千人的会上作了报告，会后收到来信70封。根据这些意见又加修改，成为现在的稿子。同时送上郭沫若、茅盾、何其芳、袁水拍、胡森胎来信五件。关于俞平伯的一段，袁水拍、何其芳提了意见，有的同志主张将这段删去。但因为这一段的影响是好的，所以仍旧保留。1956年6月13日，这篇讲话稿在《人民日报》发表。"}],"contents":[{"id":"47ce8cdfde","type":"title","text":"对《百花齐放，百家争鸣一文的批语叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901"},{"id":"3d289bafad","type":"paragraph","text":"退陆定一同志。此件很好，可以发表。在第九页上作了一点修改，请加翻的。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901"},{"id":"6027c8d72b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901"},{"id":"cb7486bde6","type":"paragraph","text":"六月八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901"},{"id":"a90a3b42c2","type":"paragraph","text":"是否可以这样修改，请和周扬、袁水拍、何其芳等同志商量一","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901"},{"id":"51da3659dc","type":"subtitle","text":"F。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901"}],"page":{"id":"e294197576","publicationId":"maoquanji36","articleId":"fa9f55a901","start":374,"end":374}}}},"__N_SSG":true}